patthana14.11:4.1: Lokiyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. #1
patthana14.11:5.1: Lokuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.11:5.2: Lokuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokiyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.11:5.3: (Lokuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokiyo ca nalokuttaro ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.) #3
patthana14.11:6.1: Lokiyañca lokuttarañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.11:7.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve … pe … avigate pañca.
